      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> (1 comment)\n > \n > It's good to add this test, but it can't stop creating regular\n > files, especially if DoM or PFL is not supported, otherwise it\n > would just fail without ever creating any files.\n\nIt does create regular file with default layout when the strip count equals to zero.\n\nracer is not part of acceptance test, I'm not sure if anybody would run this with different version of servers. I will fix it anyway.",
